Package ch.ethz.vizzly

Class Summary
AggregationLevelLookup This class calculates the returned level of detail for a request.
CsvOutputGenerator This class generates the CSV outputs that are then sent to a client.
OverlayHeatMap This class implements a first test of generating images that are then put over the map.
SamplingRateEstimation This class implements a data structure that maintains monthly estimates of the unknown (mean) sampling interval of a signal.
VizzlyServlet This class implements the servlet to which all HTTP requests are routed.
VizzlyServletContextListener This class takes care of background cache updater threads and the initialization of state that must be persisted during the lifetime of the servlet
VizzlyStateContainer This class contains all state that is needed to run the application.
